<div class="fn" id="T5FN1">
<sup>*</sup><p class="display-inline">Range is based on comparing incidence rates of 28.0 to 42.8 events per 1,000 person-years in our study cohort with 9.8 to 16.6 events per 1,000 person-years in a comparable elderly cohort.<sup><a href="#R25" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="R25">25</a></sup></p>
</div>
<div class="fn" id="T5FN2">
